#MOBILES
#13000
kowloon brawler~
A brawler~
A kowloon brawler stands before you, awaiting a fight.
~
This man is here looking for a fight. Tapping his club in his hands, he
slowly grins at you and approaches. He wears a dirty blue shirt and
some faded blue jeans with holes in them.  The only piece of clothing
that looks like its worth anything is the fine neck-chain he wears.
The club in his hands appears to have many dents and the wood is somewhat
warped in certain places. Obviously this wont be his first fight.
~
