#13001
kowloon mangler~
The mangler~
A kowloon mangler lurks in the shadows, waiting to strike.
~
This man fades in and out of view. His trusty dagger in his left hand
suggest the quick killing approach, slicing the neck. He wears a brown
T-shirt, a pair of decent looking shoes and some odd leather sleeves
to protect his forearms. He seems to have an interest in your presence
as he begins to approach you quite rapidly. By the look in his face,
its not for a friendly gathering either.
~
