#13002
kowloon convict~
The convict~
An escaped kowloon convict runs at you, trying to find shelter.
~
This man is dressed in the usual zebra striped outfit from head to toe.
The shackles on his hands suggest that this man just might not be on
parole. He runs at a very quick pace straight at you, either to run you
down or run away from someone else. Either way..it would be a good
idea to just move out of his way.
~
