#13003
kowloon ex-con~
The ex-convict~
A kowloon ex-convict is here, pimping his new look.
~
This man just made bail and is out on the town. For someone that comes
out of jail with no money, he sure is dressed in some pretty expensive
type clothing. He wears a remarkable ring on is left hand, you assume
its 14k and as you take a closer look, its covered in diamonds.
The rest of this clothing isn't too shabby, probably too good for
this man. He walks very confident past you, glaring in your direction
as he moves.
~
