kowloon drug dealer~
The drug dealer~
A kowloon drug dealer is here, offering some goods to you.
~
This man makes a living out of selling drugs. And I guess he figures that
doing some of the stuff he sells is a pretty good deal also. He's dressed
in very fancy, flashy clothing. He wears a nice leather overcoat and
has a needle in his right hand. Either he's about to shoot up ..or already
has. Finally, the nice casual hat kinda give off the fact he's a fan of
the local baseball team.
~
